
Ranger Help for: impale
=======================

SYNTAX:      impale <target>
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   11
BASE SP:     90 sp
SKILL TYPE:  attack

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to punish an opponent by impaling his or
her weapon through their opponent's armour into their body, causing 
good damage. The Ranger must use a pierce type weapon in order to 
perform this attack.

